[h1]v0.1.0 — Initial release[/h1]
First public release of Better Vehicle Dynamics for Project Zomboid Build 42.18.

[list]
[*]Torque-curve driven acceleration with a tunable low-speed shove.
[*]Surface- and weather-aware grip: independent road / rain / snow / off-road traction.
[*]Tyre-type grip model — worn / standard / modern tyres differ per surface.
[*]Load affects handling (sandbox-tunable launch penalty) and fuel use.
[*]Configurable air drag and rolling resistance (road and off-road).
[*]Opt-in researched power & weight table; public API for modded vehicles.
[*]Cargo-capacity rescale by body type.
[*]Arcade drift mode (off by default, bindable key).
[*]Tyre marks that fade out on their own.
[*]Docked vehicle info panel.
[*]Server-side ground-clip guard (multiplayer sink-into-floor safety net).
[*]Grouped sandbox pages + tuning presets.
[/list]

Requires the one-time manual Java install — see the mod description.
